Project Summary
The repo is a full-stack web app for streamlining social media tasks like cross-platform reposting and scheduling. It automates formatting posts for sites like Twitter, Facebook, Instagram, and LinkedIn using AI, targeting businesses, influencers, or devs handling multiple accounts.

Core Features
Automated Reposting: One-click share across platforms with auto-adjustments.
Smart Scheduling: Time posts for global time zones.
API Integration: Handles Twitter, Facebook, Instagram, LinkedIn quirks.
Scalable Design: Microservices for easy expansion.

Component	& Technologies
Backend-Node.js (microservices)
Frontend-Vue.js
Infrastructure-Nginx, RabbitMQ, Docker
Deployment-Docker Compose
